concerned restored to their roles.</p> <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/fashion/2020/apr/30/victoria-beckham-reverses-decision-to-furlough-fashion-label-staff">Continue reading...</a>";s:8:"category";s:50:"FashionVictoria BeckhamCoronavirus outbreakUK news";s:7:"pubdate";s:29:"Thu, 30 Apr 2020 15:01:55 GMT";s:4:"guid";s:114:"https://www.theguardian.com/fashion/2020/apr/30/victoria-beckham-reverses-decision-to-furlough-fashion-label-staff";s:5:"media";a:2:{s:7:"content";s:18:"
        
