 5ft 11in pick-and-roll savant became the first ever player – male or female – to surpass 2,000 points, 1,000 assists and 1,000 rebounds, while her 26 career triple-doubles shattered the previous record of 12 held by BYU’s Kyle Collinsworth.</p> <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2020/apr/30/sabrina-ionescu-new-york-liberty-interview">Continue reading...</a>";s:8:"category";s:60:"WNBABasketballSportUS sportsCollege basketballCollege sports";s:7:"pubdate";s:29:"Thu, 30 Apr 2020 14:30:00 GMT";s:4:"guid";s:88:"https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2020/apr/30/sabrina-ionescu-new-york-liberty-interview";s:5:"media";a:2:{s:7:"content";s:18:"
        
