ya-ceasefire-ends-recent-surge-violence">Continue reading...</a>";s:8:"category";s:49:"LibyaAfricaMiddle East and North AfricaWorld news";s:7:"pubdate";s:29:"Thu, 30 Apr 2020 17:23:08 GMT";s:4:"guid";s:96:"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/apr/30/ramadan-libya-ceasefire-ends-recent-surge-violence";s:5:"media";a:2:{s:7:"content";s:18:"
        
