an of numerous musical romances</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/apr/30/rishi-kapoor-cherubic-child-star-who-became-an-indefatigable-leading-man">Peter Bradshaw on Rishi Kapoor: cherubic child star who became an indefatigable leading man</a></li></ul><p>The Indian actor Rishi Kapoor, who built a career as one of Bollywood’s romantic heroes, has died of leukaemia at the age of 67.</p><p>Kapoor, part of a famous Bollywood family, was admitted to hospital in Mumbai on Wednesday and died on Thursday, according to a family statement.</p> <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/apr/30/rishi-kapoor-bollywood-leading-man-dies-of-leukaemia-aged-67">Continue reading...</a>";s:8:"category";s:57:"BollywoodFilmCultureIndiaWorld newsSouth and Central Asia";s:7:"pubdate";s:29:"Thu, 30 Apr 2020 07:23:31 GMT";s:4:"guid";s:105:"https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/apr/30/rishi-kapoor-bollywood-leading-man-dies-of-leukaemia-aged-67";s:5:"media";a:2:{s:7:"content";s:18:"
        
