/17/2020-election-candidates-list-democrats-primaries-trump-bernie-sanders-joe-biden-elizabeth-warren-kamala-harris-beto-o-rourke-running">Who are the 2020 candidates?</a></li><li><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2019/jun/12/us-election-2020-simple-guide-electoral-college-primaries">2020: a simple guide</a></li></ul> <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/video/2020/apr/21/could-trump-delay-the-2020-us-election-due-to-coronavirus-video-explainer">Continue reading...</a>";s:8:"category";s:86:"US elections 2020Coronavirus outbreakDonald TrumpJoe BidenUS politicsUS newsWorld news";s:7:"pubdate";s:29:"Tue, 21 Apr 2020 12:30:15 GMT";s:4:"guid";s:127:"https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/video/2020/apr/21/could-trump-delay-the-2020-us-election-due-to-coronavirus-video-explainer";s:5:"media";a:2:{s:7:"content";s:18:"
        
